improve restoring last application state.

title: Refactor PlayerService. Add handling of becoming noisy event. Add  pause/resume…
message:
Refactor PlayerService. Add handling of becoming noisy event. Add  pause/resume of stream. Add media button handling. Add transient focus lost handling.

Move player implementation details behind PlayerWrapper interface. Add RadioPlayer which now controls proxy and PlayerWrapper, RadioPlayer should be used to play streams.

Fix issue when proxy connected after being stopped.

Remove 'useExo' parameter from PlayerService 'PlayUrl' method because what player to use is deducible in PlayerService.

Fix the mess with threads in PlayerService, one spawning thread had never stopping looper, other threads spawned uncontrollably. Now there is one thread for running players.
